s.toByteArray();\n    }\n\n    private static final class NonSerializablePayload {\n        private final String name;\n\n        private NonSerializablePayload(String name) {\n            this.name = name;\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public String toString() {\n            return name;\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777677570842}, {"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_c67MRChGNpw9t8cbJ2UPrBzE|fc_07aa88f14cda3a930169f53502614481a192144d51acfc0ed7", "toolName": "read", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "/*\n * Copyright and related rights waived via CC0\n *\n * You should have received a copy of the CC0 legalcode along with this\n * work. If not, see <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>.\n */\nplugins {\n    id \"org.graalvm.internal.tck\"\n}\n\nString libraryVersion = tck.testedLibraryVersion.get()\n\ndependencies {\n    testImplementation \"org.apache.commons:commons-math3:$libraryVersion\"\n    testImplementation 'org.assertj:assertj-core:3.22.0'\n}\n\ngraalvmNative {\n    agent {\n        defaultMode = \"conditional\"\n        modes {\n            conditional {\n                userCodeFilterPath = \"user-code-filter.json\"\n            }\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777677570842}, {"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_NLbFcUJwbLPhSaHUR5afAUhZ|fc_07aa88f14cda3a930169f53502614c81a1bb38beb096ad0287", "toolName": "read", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge5/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/2727-a2260598/local_repositories/source_context/org.apache.commons/commons-math3/3.1.1/main/extracted/org/apache/commons/math3/linear/MatrixUtils.java'"}], "details": {}, "isError": true, "timestamp": 1777677570842}, {"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_lHPuNjorCBOvqdUWJ4K8bGCq|fc_07aa88f14cda3a930169f53502615481a1a5e9815754821ccd", "toolName": "read", "content": [{"t